						<br />
						<br />
						<br />
					</CardContent>
				</Card>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        		<p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
					I have been a golf instructor teaching women how to hit clubs for over 2 years. 
					I’m a passionate golfer who enjoys sharing my love of the game.
				</p>
				<hr />
				<p class="text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
					I have been a golf instructor teaching women how to hit clubs for over 2 years. 
					I’m a passionate golfer who enjoys sharing my love of the game.
				</p>
