					I’m a passionate golfer who enjoys sharing my love of the game.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- What I Offer Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-emerald-50">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-blue-500 mb-10">What I Offer</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">Private Lessons</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">One-on-one coaching tailored to your goals and skill level.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">Group Clinics</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">Small group sessions focused on fun and fundamentals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">Course Management</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">Play smarter with strategy sessions on the course.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 py-16 text-center bg-emerald-100">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-blue-500 mb-10">Step Up Your Golf Game</h2>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-neutral-700 mb-10">Professional golf instruction designed specifically for women of all skill levels.</p>
	  <div class="mb-10"	
